{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Those girls-- I was under the bed, again, or behind-- there was, like, I remember, like, a window with something there with a very old-- not a blind, or was it something-- torn blind and a curtain-- something like an old, colorful curtain.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was hidden, or they put me there, covered, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They hoped for the best.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know even if they thought what they were going to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the thing is that the roll calls were taking place, and the, the work had to be done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because we did-- we did this-- you know, the, the clothing that was coming-- there was coming clothing from Dutch Jews-- very exclusive clothes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had to select-- we were going through-- we were separating certain things from certain items.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we-- because-- how the-- one told the other, so we assumed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told that this is-- because it was silk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The underwear were many silk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And apparently somebody there who could read Dutch, who could read-- and they read it, apparently, on the labels or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody there, because I wasn't by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we had to do whatever-- they had to do whatever presented itself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, to clean the German quarters, like, to do, do the washing for the men-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All of this had to be done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whilst I was hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't ask me how they did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this was not it yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But each time, a few men I know were involved in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you see, life in camp was such-- it was going at such a pace that you really didn't have time to stop and to, you know, to really think or to really know how and what and when.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
